Usage: reportCongestion [-help] [-3d] [-hotSpot] [-includeBlockage]
                        [-num_hotspot <integer>] [-overflow]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-3d                        # honor 3d congestion map (bool, optional)
-hotSpot                   # report max and total hotSpot area (bool, optional)
-includeBlockage           # include blockage area in hotspot report
                           # (bool, optional)
-num_hotspot <integer>     # specify number of hotspots to be reported
                           # (int, optional)
-overflow                  # report horizontal and vertical overflow
                           # (bool, optional)